; Addresses are module offsets (load segment 0, i.e. file offset minus the
; 0x3200 MZ header). The trace reaches 10 routines / 1011 bytes and then stops
; at the C-runtime's indirect handoff into the game proper — the game's own
; startup runs in overlay-paged and relocated segments whose file bytes differ
; from their run-time content, so it cannot be traced statically. Those routines
; are documented, with the addresses the execution-core oracle pinned at run
; time, in uw.annotations.txt.
;
; See ../Ultima_Underworld.md Part II §3 and Part III for the narrative.
; ============================================================================

